        <div class="body">
            <p>There are no examples in the manual either showing how to do the following example using a Zend_Db instance using the PDO_MYSQL adapter.</p>

<p>Example 3. Call a stored procedure with an INOUT parameter</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>&lt;?php
/* Call a stored procedure with an INOUT parameter */
$colour = 'red';
$sth = $dbh-&gt;prepare('CALL puree_fruit(?)');
$sth-&gt;bindParam(1, $colour, PDO::PARAM_STR|PDO::PARAM_INPUT_OUTPUT, 12);
$sth-&gt;execute();
print("After pureeing fruit, the colour is: $colour");
?&gt;
</code></pre>

